SELECT TOP(2) [s].[Value]
FROM (
    SELECT CAST(ISNULL(SUM(p.[rows]), 0) AS int) AS [Value]
      FROM sys.partitions p
      WHERE p.object_id = OBJECT_ID(N'[dbo].[Patient]')
        AND p.index_id IN (0, 1)
) AS [s]

FROM (

SELECT TOP(2) [s].[Value]
FROM (
    SELECT CAST(ISNULL(SUM(p.[rows]), 0) AS int) AS [Value]
      FROM sys.partitions p
      WHERE p.object_id = OBJECT_ID(N'[dbo].[Service_Line]')

) AS [s]

SELECT TOP(2) [s].[Value]
FROM (
    SELECT CAST(ISNULL(SUM(p.[rows]), 0) AS int) AS [Value]
      FROM sys.partitions p
      WHERE p.object_id = OBJECT_ID(N'[dbo].[Service_Line]')
        AND p.index_id IN (0, 1)
) AS [s]

2026-01-30 16:18:11.634 +05:30 [ERR] Failed executing DbCommand (35,012ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(2) [s].[Value]
FROM (
    SELECT CAST(ISNULL(SUM(p.[rows]), 0) AS int) AS [Value]
      FROM sys.partitions p
      WHERE p.object_id = OBJECT_ID(N'[dbo].[Service_Line]')
        AND p.index_id IN (0, 1)
) AS [s]

    INNER JOIN [Patient] AS [p] ON [c].[ClaPatFID] = [p].[PatID]
    INNER JOIN [Physician] AS [p0] ON [c].[ClaRenderingPhyFID] = [p0].[PhyID]
    INNER JOIN [Physician] AS [p1] ON [c].[ClaReferringPhyFID] = [p1].[PhyID]

) AS [s0]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[SrvID], [s].[SrvFromDate], [s].[SrvToDate], [s].[SrvProcedureCode], [s].[SrvDesc], [s].[SrvCharges], [s].[SrvUnits], [s].[SrvPlace], [s].[SrvDiagnosisPointer], [s].[SrvTotalBalanceCC], [s].[SrvTotalAmtPaidCC], [s].[SrvTotalAdjCC], [s].[SrvTotalAmtAppliedCC], [s].[SrvResponsibleParty], [p4].[PayName], [p4].[PayID], [s1].[AdjID], [s1].[AdjDate], [s1].[AdjAmount], [s1].[AdjGroupCode], [s1].[AdjReasonCode], [s1].[AdjDateTimeCreated], [s1].[PayerName], [s1].[PayID] AS [PayID0], [s2].[PmtID], [s2].[PmtDate], [s2].[PmtAmount], [s2].[PmtMethod], [s2].[Pmt835Ref], [s2].[PmtDateTimeCreated], [s].[SrvClaFID]

        FROM [Adjustment] AS [a0]

        WHERE [s].[SrvID] = [a0].[AdjSrvFID]

) AS [s3] ON [s0].[ClaID] = [s3].[SrvClaFID]
